<i>adverb</i>: 평온히 [평온히], 태연히 [태연히], 태연스레 [태연스레], 침착히 [침차키], 착 [착], 조용히 [조용히], 잠잠히 [잠잠히], 잔잔히 [잔잔히], 유연히 [유연히], 씨근씨근 [씨근씨근], 쌔근쌔근 [쌔근쌔근], 덤덤히 [덤덤히], 담담히 [담ː담히], 냉정히 [냉ː정히], 고요히 [고요히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평온히 [평온히]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; quietly; serenely</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없고 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly without any worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>태연히 [태연히]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; coolly; self-possessedly</dd><br>
<dd>당연히 머뭇거리거나 두려워할 상황에서 태도나 얼굴빛이 아무렇지도 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an attitude or complexion in which one shows no difference in a situation in which one is expected to hesitate or be scared.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>태연스레 [태연스레]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; coolly; self-possessedly</dd><br>
<dd>당연히 머뭇거리거나 두려워할 상황에서 태도나 얼굴빛이 아무렇지도 않은 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an attitude or complexion in which one shows no difference in a situation in which one is expected to hesitate or be scared.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>침착히 [침차키]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; coolly; composedly</dd><br>
<dd>쉽게 흥분하지 않고 행동이 조심스럽고 차분하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Carefully and calmly in one's action, not being excited easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>착 [착]</dt><br>
<dd>1. calmly</dd><br>
<dd>몸가짐이나 태도가 얌전하고 태연한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's behavior or attitude being quiet and composed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. droopingly</dd><br>
<dd>조금 느슨하게 휘어지거나 늘어진 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of hanging low or bending loosely.</dd><br>
<dd>3. droopingly</dd><br>
<dd>몸에 힘이 없어 늘어진 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's body sagging due to a lack of energy.</dd><br>
<dd>4. gloomily</dd><br>
<dd>분위기나 감정 등이 어둡고 우울한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of an atmosphere, emotion, etc., being dark and depressed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. in a low manner</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 내리깔거나 목소리를 낮게 내는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of lowering one's gaze or voice.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조용히 [조용히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>아무 소리도 들리지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>With no sound being heard.</dd><br>
<dd>2. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>말이 적고 행동이 얌전하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being restrained in speech and gentle in behavior.</dd><br>
<dd>3. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>문제가 없이 평안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Peacefully and without problems.</dd><br>
<dd>4. calmly</dd><br>
<dd>감정이 가라앉아 마음이 평안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With peace of mind and emotions calmed down.</dd><br>
<dd>5. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>바쁘지 않고 한가하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being free and not busy.</dd><br>
<dd>6. quietly</dd><br>
<dd>남들에게 드러나지 않게 숨어서.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being hidden and not revealed to others.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잠잠히 [잠잠히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. silently; still</dd><br>
<dd>분위기나 활동 등이 시끄럽지 않고 조용히.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an atmosphere, activity, etc., being quiet, not noisy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. silently; quietly</dd><br>
<dd>말없이 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being still without saying anything.</dd><br>
<dd>3. calmly; still</dd><br>
<dd>파도나 바람 등이 움직이지 않고 조용히.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of waves, wind, etc., being quiet without moving.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잔잔히 [잔잔히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. calmly; tranquilly; quietly</dd><br>
<dd>바람이나 물결 등이 심하지 않고 움직임이 거의 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of the wind, a wave, etc., being still and not severe.</dd><br>
<dd>2. serenely; tranquilly; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>분위기가 고요하고 평화롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an atmosphere being silent and peaceful.</dd><br>
<dd>3. calmly; serenely</dd><br>
<dd>표정이나 태도 등이 차분하고 평온하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's look, attitude, etc., being composed and peaceful.</dd><br>
<dd>4. gently</dd><br>
<dd>소리가 조용하고 부드럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a sound being quiet and soft.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>유연히 [유연히]</dt><br>
<dd>relaxedly; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>차분하고 여유가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a calm and relaxed manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>씨근씨근 [씨근씨근]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pantingly; out of breath</dd><br>
<dd>고르지 않고 거칠고 가쁘게 자꾸 숨 쉬는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating or describing the sound or manner of breathing irregularly, roughly, and hard.</dd><br>
<dd>2. calmly; peacefully</dd><br>
<dd>어린아이가 깊이 잠들어 매우 조용하게 자꾸 숨 쉬는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating or describing the sound or manner of a child breathing very quietly while sleeping.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>쌔근쌔근 [쌔근쌔근]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pantingly; out of breath</dd><br>
<dd>조금 거칠게 자꾸 숨 쉬는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating or describing the sound or manner of breathing a little roughly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. calmly; peacefully</dd><br>
<dd>어린아이가 깊이 잠들어 조용하게 자꾸 숨 쉬는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating or describing the sound or manner of a child breathing quietly while being fast asleep.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>덤덤히 [덤덤히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. calmly; as usual</dd><br>
<dd>특별한 감정이나 느낌을 드러내지 않고 보통 때와 같이.</dd><br>
<dd>Same as usual without revealing a special emotion or feeling.</dd><br>
<dd>2. speechlessly</dd><br>
<dd>말할 자리에서 어떤 말이나 반응이 없고 무표정하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one remains still without any word, response, or facial expression, when one is expected to say something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>담담히 [담ː담히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. composedly; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>차분하고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a calm and comfortable attitude.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plainly</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 말 내용이 감정적이지 않고 객관적이게.</dd><br>
<dd>Objectively, not expressing oneself emotionally in writing or speaking.</dd><br>
<dd>3. serenely</dd><br>
<dd>물이 맑고 그 움직임이 고요하고 평온하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state such as that when clean water flows quietly and peacefully.</dd><br>
<dd>4. plainly</dd><br>
<dd>맛이 짜거나 느끼하지 않고 산뜻하고 싱겁게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of tasting fresh and insipid, not salty or greasy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>냉정히 [냉ː정히]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; composedly</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 행동이 감정에 좌우되지 않고 침착하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's thinking or behavior being composed and not swayed by one's emotions.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고요히 [고요히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. silently</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽거나 어지럽지 않고 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly, neither noisily nor confusedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. serenely; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>강이나 바다 등의 물결이 잔잔하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a river, the sea, etc., flowing with small ripples.</dd><br>
<dd>3. peacefully; serenely</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 상태 등이 조용하고 평화롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a quiet and peaceful mind or in such a state.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>